<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Your Verification Code</title>
  <style>
    body { margin:0; padding:0; background:#f4f6f9; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color:#333; }
    .container { max-width:560px; margin:40px auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background:#1a3c6e; padding:32px 40px; text-align:center; }
    .header h1 { color:#ffffff; margin:0; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.5px; }
    .header p { color:#b8cce4; margin:4px 0 0; font-size:13px; }
    .body { padding:40px; }
    .greeting { font-size:16px; color:#444; margin-bottom:20px; }
    .otp-box { background:#f0f4ff; border:2px solid #1a3c6e; border-radius:10px; padding:28px; text-align:center; margin:28px 0; }
    .otp-code { font-size:42px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:12px; color:#1a3c6e; font-family:monospace; }
    .otp-label { font-size:12px; color:#7a8ba8; margin-top:8px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; }
    .expiry-note { background:#fff8e1; border-left:4px solid #f59e0b; padding:12px 16px; border-radius:4px; font-size:14px; color:#92400e; margin-bottom:24px; }
    .security-note { font-size:13px; color:#9ca3af; padding:20px 0; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb; margin-top:24px; }
    .footer { background:#f4f6f9; padding:20px 40px; text-align:center; font-size:12px; color:#9ca3af; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>{{institution_name}}</h1>
      <p>Powered by FuhsoX</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p class="greeting">Hello, Scholar 👋</p>
      <p>Use the verification code below to sign in to your account. This code is valid for <strong>{{expiry_minutes}} minutes</strong>.</p>

      <div class="otp-box">
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp_code}}</div>
        <div class="otp-label">One-Time Verification Code</div>
      </div>

      <div class="expiry-note">
        ⏰ This code expires in <strong>{{expiry_minutes}} minutes</strong>. If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.
      </div>

      <div class="security-note">
        🔒 <strong>Security tip:</strong> FuhsoX will never ask for this code via phone, chat, or any other channel. Only enter it on the official FuhsoX login page. If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email — your account is safe.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} {{institution_name}} &middot; Powered by FuhsoX &middot; All rights reserved
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
